ex02: NDC2RGB shader

Willem A. (Vlakkies) Schreuder
CSCI4239/5239 Spring 2026

Map NDC [-1,+1] to RGB [0,1]


Key bindings
  m          Toggle shaders
  o          Change objects
  xXyYzZ     Change location
  arrows     Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit
